data: My wallet was stolen last week and they sent a replacement that begins with 3782; I want to know if I have to use the same PIN to activate that replacement card or if a new PIN will be issued, so tell me plainly Ã¢â‚¬â€ I don't want to be bounced around.
SELECT T1.*, T2.* FROM customers AS T1 LEFT JOIN cards AS T2 ON T1.customer_id = T2.customer_id WHERE T1.customer_id = 'C003' AND (substr(REPLACE(T2.card_number, '-', ''), 1, 4) = '3782');
